Overwine Hall: Foes of the Free People
Foes of the Free Peoples found at Overwine Hall should be defeated in order protect those within the Wildwood.
Foes can be found at Overwine Hall in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should defeat foes at Overwine Hall.
Foes of the Free Peoples have claimed the ruins of Overwine Hall within the Wildwood. Defeating their numbers here will assist in returning safety to the Wildwood.
